🧬 Cancer is never random; it’s communication.

Dolores Cannon spent decades speaking directly with the Higher Self through thousands of QHHT sessions. Again and again, the body revealed something profound: when emotions like anger are suppressed, unspoken, or buried for years, they don’t disappear, they store themselves in the body.
Not as punishment… but as a signal.
A call for acknowledgment, compassion, and truth.

In this rare interview, Dolores shares what the body itself has expressed about cancer and why healing begins when we allow ourselves to feel, speak, and listen within.

✨ What if your body has been trying to protect you all along?

